 * { series, category, value, index } on hover/focus of a point.
 *
 * CSP-safe, dependency-free (only lit). Owned source, copied in by `lievit add chart`.
 * Light-DOM rendered so Tailwind + `--lv-*` tokens cascade in.
 */
